    "name": "星际卡车司机",
    "steam_appid": 2380050,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380050/extras/b875f73e4c652c951a7473ca4b018899.poster.avif?t=1769517827\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380050/extras/b875f73e4c652c951a7473ca4b018899.webm?t=1769517827\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380050/extras/b875f73e4c652c951a7473ca4b018899.mp4?t=1769517827\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>爬上驾驶位，开着火箭驱动的大车，拖运货物，寻找需要捞救的货品，邂逅光怪陆离的星际货运司机。驶入太空这条终极大道，踏上颇具亚美利加风情的旅途！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380050/extras/Haul_Holler_v2.png?t=1769517827\" /></span><br><br>漫游超级公路，承接各类委托。从耗油量极大的长途到兵行险着的送货任务，辛苦跑车挣钱，享受解锁新内容的单纯快乐。<br><br>时刻关注民用无线电，听同行说说闲话，敏锐捕捉兼职信息与星际八卦。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380050/extras/1e1ac4a21f0d16b2a78338ed21fa5855.poster.avif?t=1769517827\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380050/extras/1e1ac4a21f0d16b2a78338ed21fa5855.webm?t=1769517827\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380050/extras/1e1ac4a21f0d16b2a78338ed21fa5855.mp4?t=1769517827\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380050/extras/2f95ecd78430a8962212fef2d2f48c08.avif?t=1769517827\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br><br>开大车真不是件容易事，保证核心系统和重力补偿器正常运行的同时，车身也得修修补补，驾驶室漏了馅可就糟糕了。<br><br>出发前，记得去当地的汽修厂更换好零部件，适时进行一些升级。不断优化驾驶工具，才能保证安全驶过不稳定区域，准时送达货物。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380050/extras/0d494dd99442002b31b91c9f9e00ba18.avif?t=1769517827\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br><br>参照银河系地图，规划行程，在燃料储备充足、动力水平强劲的情况下，实现曲速跃迁。<br><br>设定好路线之后，你大可以优哉游哉地打开驾驶室内的高保真音响，在各色原创歌曲的陪伴下畅游宇宙。耳边是星爆蓝调、银河摇滚和行星乡村，还不赶紧启动卡车，朝着眼前一望无际的星际公路出发？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380050/extras/6f62ffe28bc7fc6936bbc6b95afe8dcb.avif?t=1769517827\" width=1560 height=253 /></span><br><br>《星际卡车司机》是 Monster and Monster 团队的心血之作。这个二人独立工作室对所有科幻和模拟类的东西都爱得深沉。<br><br>在实力好友的帮助下，他们打造出了一种前所未有的游戏体验，既要应对层出不穷的挑战，也要掌握形形色色的复杂系统。系好安全带，一起踏上货运之旅吧！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380050/extras/c7cfd82d7137f3062c5234b10d116d3f.poster.avif?t=1769517827\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380050/extras/c7cfd82d7137f3062c5234b10d116d3f.webm?t=1769517827\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380050/extras/c7cfd82d7137f3062c5234b10d116d3f.mp4?t=1769517827\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
